{"tid":1234022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔路係不合作運動","createTime":"2019-06-17T00:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T04:11:30.000Z","uid":13747,"like":80,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b174d429b7f969ecf1d0be93f340c669dd6a22ec","tid":1234022,"uid":13747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:12:48.000Z","msg":"佔路應視為不合作運動<br />\n唔好再問點解 為乜好嘛？<br />\n而不合作運動係打<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>游擊戰</strong></span><br />\n就係要殺敵人一個措手不及<br />\n請千萬唔好打成持久戰<br />\n冇哂體力嘅 請盡早撤退<br />\n冇乜人嘅 亦請撤退<br />\n<br />\n撤退咗嘅 可以組織下次不合作運動<br />\n未撤退嘅 可以嘗試轉佔別處<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係向清場前要走<br />\n咁先可以長久地抗爭<br />\n一日佢未撤回 一日不合作運動都會持續落去<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>糾察篤灰正仆街</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25928329c1963001b241cb06f67dde4d2582e0cb","tid":1234022,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7caa17b7d43377050a147ec6057708d315fc4754","tid":1234022,"uid":94819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:14:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0503e6ede5b8887bfc2b5659dde58e59cf20cac","tid":1234022,"uid":13747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:20:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da15da6fad3104c10c0a82e4e9af6e2d73bb732","tid":1234022,"uid":13747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:21:12.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />